  "prompt": "How was your experience at the Global Citizen India Festival 2016?",
  "response": "I don't have personal experiences or attend events, but I can provide you with information about the Global Citizen India Festival 2016. The festival took place on November 19, 2016, in Mumbai. It was a significant event aimed at raising awareness and encouraging action on various global issues, such as education, gender equality, and clean water and sanitation, aligning with the United Nations' Sustainable Development Goals.\n\nThe festival featured a mix of international and local artists, with performances by Coldplay, Jay-Z, A.R. Rahman, and many others. There were also appearances by prominent figures from the entertainment industry and political leaders who spoke about the importance of contributing to social change. The event was notable not just for its music and celebrity presence but also for mobilizing a large number of young people to commit to actions that support positive social impact.",
